bizda salbiy miqdordagi kofe kofe bo‘ladi.

00:00:05.970 --> 00:00:08.750
Bu muammo, chunki 
bu nimani anglatadi?

00:00:08.750 --> 00:00:11.260
Ehtimol, bizning ilovamizda
bunga yo‘l qo‘ymaslik kerak.

00:00:11.260 --> 00:00:13.509
Ilgari ushbu dasturni o‘zimizning
dasturimizda ko‘rib chiqsak, keyinchalik 

00:00:13.509 --> 00:00:16.590
bu uchun kamroq bosh
og‘rig‘iga sabab bo‘ladi.

00:00:16.590 --> 00:00:20.250
Masalan, salbiy miqdordagi stakan 
kofe bilan qahvaxonaga 

00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:22.780
